--------------------------------------------
Usage: huxley mixin [subcommand] [name]
--------------------------------------------
Follow any command with "help" for more information.

This sub-command allows you to add services to your application.  Each named mixin
adds a subdirectory to your application's "launch/" directory.  This contains a
template ready for your configuration and will ultimately be launched into its own
Linux container.

Available Mixins:

  elasticsearch
  kibana
  redis

Available Mixin Subcommands:

  add, create
  remove, rm, delete, destroy
